# HEX ONLY (read-safe). display-deception canary: the canary token with Cyrillic
# homoglyphs (O->U+041E, A->U+0410) -- it READS as 'POC-CORPUS-CANARY-FIRED' but is a
# distinct string. A neutralizing terminal reveals/marks the non-ASCII code points.
